description:
On a spectacular birthday episode of Unqualified, Rob Riggle (21 JUMP STREET, THE HANGOVER, STEP BROTHERS) joins Anna and Sim to try his signature vodka (6:30) and talk about the worst job he's ever had (22:20)! They also play some deal breakers (28:30) and a quick round of How Would You Proceed? (45:00)

Later, they call Amanda (54:30) who's boyfriend planned to go to a concert on her birthday without telling her, and Delia (1:06:30) who needs help finding a Christmas gift for her boyfriend who seems to have everything he needs. Don't miss it!

 

Social Media: Rob Riggle: @RobRiggle Anna Faris: @annafaris Unqualified: @unqualified
